    <id>linkboard</id>
    <name>LinkBoard</name>
    <summary>Personal service dashboard inspired by Gethomepage</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[
**LinkBoard** – A beautiful, customizable service dashboard for your homelab.

Organize your services in categories, monitor their status,
and access everything from within Nextcloud.

### Features
- 🏠 Personal dashboard with service tiles grouped by category
- 🎨 Dark/Light mode with customizable backgrounds
- 🖼️ Flexible icon system (upload, URL, Material Design Icons)
- 📋 YAML & JSON import/export (Gethomepage compatible)
- 🔍 Quick search across all services
- 📂 Nested categories with drag & drop grouping
- ✏️ Inline editing with drag & drop sorting
- 🩺 Service health checks with status indicators
- 📈 Status history with response time charts and uptime tracking
- 📊 Widget system for live data from external APIs

Each user gets their own personal dashboard – up to 500 services.
    ]]></description>
